description: Your websites Colormind and Humint work great and are very helpful, at least there's that, but the app doesn't seem to generate anything from the web, unless you input the values yourself, which defeats the purpose. I will continue to use the websites, and once the app is working, I'll try it again. Great concept though.
I generated few colors for website based on my two previous picked colors. Sowtware helped me to generate 3 more colors that fit into my previous pick.
summary: App is pretty good. Easy to use and works great
